line_1: For her forbears were brought in ships,
line_2: She was nae get o' moorlan tips,

line_1: For her forbears were brought in ships,
line_2: Wi' tauted ket, an' hairy hips;

line_1: For her forbears were brought in ships,
line_2: A bonier fleesh ne'er cross'd the clips
Nor grace our Northern names her lips,

line_1: When Tydings came, his ill-provided Ships
line_2: This idle Vaunt had scarcely past his Lips,
